      "span_text": "For EPR experiments, AFA-PLN with the TOAC spin label substituted at 11, 24, or 36 was synthesized and reconstituted into lipid vesicles containing DOPC: DOPE (4:1, 200 lipids per PLN).  EPR spectra were acquired using a Bruker ELEXSYS 500 spectrometer with the SHQ cavity."
