      "span_text": "EPR spectra were simulated as a sum of one or two components, each component produced by a population having a static random distribution of membrane orientations and undergoing rotational diffusion in a restricting potential (defined by order parameter S) with a single rotational correlation time.  Experimental spectra were fit by summing simulated components, yielding mole fractions."
